text: Attal is a consanguineous namesake associated with the Maheshwari caste, However they often tried to reclaim higher status of Jat (_Kshatriya_) background but remained unsatisfactory, Due having a strong affinity with other subordinating Vaishya groups. == Related pages == * Namesake * Trader * Vaishya * Suraj Mal == References == Category:Castes
title: Attal (caste)
